$interpreted: Karnulla: Huh! YOU, always hindering with our hunting! I'll never have to worry again, if I get rid of you ONCE AND FOR ALL!
Pang: Karnulla, STOP!
Karnulla: What, going under the sea and to the mermaid's side this time?
Pang: No. I acknowledge your plight for survival, but if vendetta is driving your intent to kill...
Pang: I cannot let you do that!
Karnulla: Put a sock in it!
Hestia: Well done! Bullies like these need to be taught a lesson! Let me at him, I'll land the final blow!
Pang: Hestia, let him go.
Hestia: Pang, didn't you come to help me?
Pang: I don't wish to see my friends hurt each other. Besides, the frogodiles have their way of life.
Pang: You shouldn't interfere with their nature!
Hestia: YOU!
Karnulla: Are you pitying me?
Pang: I'm making a choice that I won't come to regret.
Pang: Also, you can't bear a grudge forever. Make amends with Yan-Bo.
Karnulla: Nonsense! I admit defeat but this won't happen again. Bambinos, turn tail!
Hestia: How could you let that bully go? How could you? I'm absolutely mortified. We are friends no longer!
Puggi: Whoa~ Happy Hestia seems really ticked off...
Yan-Bo: Never fear. Despite spewing words of hate, not bad at heart, these two.
Pang: Master Yan-Bo, have I made the right decision?

Yan-Bo: A fool thinks himself to be wise,
but a wise man knows himself to be a fool.
Lord, what fools these mortals be.
Yan-Bo: Most importantly, stop any bloodshed you did. Worth commemorating, that itself is.
Pang: Yet, no way to go back in time and start over...
Pang: Not again!
Yan-Bo: Rotten to the core, that fruit is. What shall you do?
Pang: Needless to say, to throw it away.
Yan-Bo: YES. Leave it be, return to nature, the fruit will. Seeds grow into trees, its own new life begins.
Pang: Speaking of that, I've never took the time to properly appreciate these maples of the lake. Ah, what a sight to behold, so entrancing...
Yan-Bo: The road ahead is long, the future far away. Now journey, live in the moment.
Pang: Master Yan-bo, why have you bestowed such kindness upon me?
Yan-Bo: Reason not need be. Together brought by fate are we.
Pang: I see you are also from the East, based on attire. You also seem to be quite familiar with the Alliance's operations, could it be...
Yan-Bo: Turn over a new leaf. These trees are of life, these maples.

Yan-Bo: So wise so young, they say, do never live long.
Some rise by sin, and some by virtue fall...
